20:48.648 --> 20:50.848
- What the hell do I have to
lose, Autumn?

20:50.850 --> 20:53.551
That fucker deserves to pay
for what he did to Cash,

20:53.553 --> 20:54.852
and to me.

20:54.854 --> 20:57.521
He has all the money, mine too.

20:57.523 --> 20:59.223
So what choice do I have?

20:59.225 --> 21:00.391
- You could just run.

21:00.393 --> 21:01.726
- And go where?

21:01.728 --> 21:04.862
I have no money, no family, no
friends.

21:05.798 --> 21:09.867
Big Ronnie has people all over
the country, criminal types.

21:09.869 --> 21:13.137
The scumbags that would slit
your throat just for fun.

21:13.139 --> 21:15.673
So he'd have everybody hunting
for me.

21:15.675 --> 21:17.875
So I'm fucked either way.

21:17.877 --> 21:20.511
At least this way, I'm calling
the shots.

21:20.513 --> 21:24.315
And it's as you said for
yourself, I'll get my revenge.

21:24.317 --> 21:26.651
- You'll call the shots, sure.

21:26.653 --> 21:29.020
But neither one of us are in
control here.

21:38.865 --> 21:42.600
(speaking foreign language)

21:46.706 --> 21:49.607
(thunder booming)

21:58.418 --> 22:00.651
Stay there without escape.

22:01.988 --> 22:07.058
Witness my darkness, my
vengeance
against your mortal flesh.

22:10.430 --> 22:10.828
Repeat this with me.

22:14.600 --> 22:18.969
- [Both] Power of anger, power
of hate.

22:18.971 --> 22:22.707
Discord brings you to your fate.

22:22.709 --> 22:27.278
Demons of anger, demons of hate.

22:27.280 --> 22:31.148
Bring him down, I will not wait.

22:31.150 --> 22:33.451
So it shall be.

22:33.453 --> 22:37.755
Vengeance now may manifest.

22:37.757 --> 22:40.124
- Here me, dark prince.

22:40.126 --> 22:41.859
Give my hatred life.

22:42.895 --> 22:45.529
Manifest to destroy my enemies.

22:47.400 --> 22:50.301
(thunder booming)

22:51.537 --> 22:54.872
Manifest to bring about my
vengeance.

22:54.874 --> 22:56.807
(sparking)

22:56.809 --> 22:59.110
(chanting)

23:03.616 --> 23:06.617
(shovel crunching)

23:11.791 --> 23:13.157
- Fill that hole, Satchel.

23:13.159 --> 23:15.259
That goes for the
rest of you guys, too.

23:15.261 --> 23:16.994
We don't anything
digging him up.

23:17.830 --> 23:19.830
(thunder booming)

23:19.832 --> 23:21.699
- Looks like a
storm's comin', boss.

23:22.935 --> 23:25.736
(dramatic music)

23:26.839 --> 23:28.105
- That doesn't look good.

23:28.107 --> 23:29.774
Come on, boys, get in the truck.

23:42.221 --> 23:46.056
(car engine sputtering)

23:46.058 --> 23:48.025
Hang on everybody.

23:48.027 --> 23:51.829
I don't know what this is, but
it's hitting us really hard.

23:51.831 --> 23:54.632
(wind whistling)
(thunder booming)

23:54.634 --> 23:56.967
(chanting)

24:04.343 --> 24:06.076
- Give me your hand.

24:09.582 --> 24:12.483
(flesh squishing)

24:16.556 --> 24:20.291
(speaking foreign language)

24:45.351 --> 24:47.751
(squishing)

25:08.541 --> 25:09.373
- Autumn!

25:09.375 --> 25:12.276
(Autumn growling)

25:17.917 --> 25:19.750
Autumn, what the fuck?

25:19.752 --> 25:23.487
(speaking foreign language)

25:37.003 --> 25:39.904
(Ronnie groaning)

25:43.609 --> 25:46.410
(Ronnie yelling)

25:58.591 --> 26:01.358
- [Autumn] Give my hatred life.

26:01.360 --> 26:04.495
Manifest to bring about my
vengeance.

26:07.066 --> 26:08.065
- My heart.

26:11.237 --> 26:14.338
(dramatic music)

26:14.340 --> 26:16.907
- [Ronnie] Hang on, everybody.

26:19.412 --> 26:20.311
- Autumn.

26:21.414 --> 26:22.313
- Oh.

26:23.149 --> 26:25.449
Fuck, this has never happened
before.

26:26.752 --> 26:30.254
Savanna, you must leave here.

26:30.256 --> 26:34.224
Go anywhere, but you cannot stay
here.

26:34.226 --> 26:35.559
Go.

26:35.561 --> 26:37.595
- But, what will I do?

26:37.597 --> 26:39.063
Where will I go?

26:39.065 --> 26:41.231
You're the only family I have
left.

26:41.233 --> 26:43.367
- Just go anywhere.

26:43.369 --> 26:45.269
Be happy.

26:45.271 --> 26:46.837
I'll find you someday.

26:49.609 --> 26:52.910
(light dramatic music)

27:05.558 --> 27:08.525
(tires screeching)

27:09.862 --> 27:11.528
- Holy hell.

27:11.530 --> 27:13.497
Is it Halloween time, already?

27:13.499 --> 27:15.165
- You got jokes.

27:15.167 --> 27:16.867
- You gotta have a huge sack of
marbles

27:16.869 --> 27:18.936
running around this area like
that.

27:18.938 --> 27:20.471
- Well, why's that?

27:20.473 --> 27:23.574
- Anyone going up and down
the road dressed as Elvis,

27:23.576 --> 27:26.143
with a guitar on his
back and this thumb out,

27:26.145 --> 27:27.978
asking for trouble in this town.

27:27.980 --> 27:28.912
- So you're telling me a brother

27:28.914 --> 27:31.348
can't enjoy some Elvis around
here?

27:31.350 --> 27:33.484
- Have you looked in
the mirror lately, man?

27:33.486 --> 27:36.954
I'd say it's a little more
than enjoying some Elvis.

27:36.956 --> 27:39.189
I'd take it, you're
playing some kinda show?

27:39.191 --> 27:41.125
- Yeah, I'm toured with a group
of guys.

27:41.127 --> 27:43.327
We performed in Vegas some years
back.

27:43.329 --> 27:45.229
My vehicle broke down about 20
miles.

27:45.231 --> 27:47.598
Local mechanic said it was a
lost cause.

27:47.600 --> 27:49.366
No one would pick my ass up.

27:50.169 --> 27:52.202
- Yeah, I wonder why.

27:53.072 --> 27:54.471
Well, hop in bud.

27:55.274 --> 27:56.306
Let's hit the road.

28:00.513 --> 28:05.582
(car engine rumbling)
(rock music)

28:12.491 --> 28:15.826
(bar patrons cheering)

28:17.930 --> 28:20.330
(whistling)

28:50.763 --> 28:52.796
- And they actually serve food
here, too?

28:52.798 --> 28:55.132
- Best Italian steak in the
state.

28:55.134 --> 28:56.767
I wouldn't steer you wrong.

28:56.769 --> 28:58.669
It's got real fresh beef.

28:58.671 --> 28:59.570
- Uh huh.

29:18.023 --> 29:20.357
- Oh, hey, just give us
a few minutes, honey.

29:22.294 --> 29:25.629
(bar patrons cheering)

29:32.104 --> 29:36.673
(bar patrons talking over each
other)

29:44.683 --> 29:46.650
- Hey, no touching, sugar.

29:46.652 --> 29:48.685
- Come on, Bambi, come on.

29:48.687 --> 29:50.354
- Hey, motherfucker, you piece
of shit.

29:50.356 --> 29:51.889
You can't be treating the girls
like that.

29:51.891 --> 29:54.191
I don't know who the fuck
you think you are, but--

29:54.193 --> 29:57.261
(bottle shattering)

29:59.732 --> 30:02.533
(fists thudding)

30:07.740 --> 30:08.639
- Thanks, man.

30:09.575 --> 30:10.407
- You better get that looked at.

30:10.409 --> 30:12.142
You might need stitches.

30:12.144 --> 30:13.777
- Nah, I'll be okay.

30:13.779 --> 30:16.547
I'm used to dealing with
this fucking piece of shit.

30:16.549 --> 30:18.782
(gasping)

30:19.652 --> 30:21.652
- I've had enough of this shit.

30:21.654 --> 30:23.520
Do you like this job?

30:23.522 --> 30:25.856
- Yes, I, (stuttering), I'm
sorry.

30:25.858 --> 30:28.959
- Kurt, why did you do
that to this motherfucker?

30:28.961 --> 30:31.395
- He got real handsy with Bambi
there.

30:31.397 --> 30:32.896
- You know he didn't mean
nothin'.

30:32.898 --> 30:34.331
- Kurt didn't do shit.

30:34.333 --> 30:36.600
I did it, he's an asshole.

30:36.602 --> 30:39.136
He comes in here every
payday, harasses us.

30:39.138 --> 30:41.538
Half the time he's sneaking
into the dressing rooms.

30:41.540 --> 30:43.774
I have had just enough, Spider.

30:43.776 --> 30:46.243
- So you've had enough of this?

30:46.245 --> 30:47.811
Well the door's that way,

30:47.813 --> 30:51.448
don't let it hit you in your
ass, baby.

30:51.450 --> 30:53.050
- Are you serious?

30:53.052 --> 30:54.818
- Hey, it's Spider, isn't it?

30:54.820 --> 30:56.920
- And who in the hell are you?

30:56.922 --> 30:58.288
- I've been coming
here for years.

30:58.290 --> 31:00.190
I love the dames, love the eats.

31:00.192 --> 31:02.426
Best Italian steak in the state,

31:02.428 --> 31:04.595
but Bambi here didn't do the
damage.

31:04.597 --> 31:05.429
I did it.

31:05.431 --> 31:07.197
- So you did this?

31:08.701 --> 31:11.001
Well I don't give two
shits who did this.

31:11.003 --> 31:13.337
This is bullshit.

31:13.339 --> 31:18.008
Get these fuckers out of here
and somebody get their ass

31:18.010 --> 31:21.378
on this bar and
start jiggling it.

31:21.380 --> 31:23.113
- Screw you, Spider.

31:23.949 --> 31:25.349
I need to get my stuff.

31:25.351 --> 31:28.385
You, you need to get a backbone.

31:33.158 --> 31:34.725
- I'm really sorry, man.

31:34.726 --> 31:36.293
You know, that fucker's my
brother-in-law

31:36.295 --> 31:37.661
and this is my only gig.

31:37.663 --> 31:40.230
And two strikes now,
you know how it is, man.

31:44.036 --> 31:45.135
I'm sorry.

31:45.136 --> 31:46.235
- Hey, thanks for what
you did in there.

31:46.238 --> 31:47.671
- Oh, hell, little lady.

31:47.673 --> 31:49.740
Hey, you had some pretty
good moves of your own.

31:49.742 --> 31:51.074
Me and Elvis here, we just
stopped in

31:51.076 --> 31:52.109
for some eats and then,

31:52.111 --> 31:54.177
then that asshole started in.

31:54.179 --> 31:55.345
- Well, I appreciate it.

31:55.347 --> 31:56.647
And I'm sorry you guys didn't
get dinner,

31:56.649 --> 31:58.649
but there is a diner
about two blocks down.

31:58.651 --> 32:01.118
- Well, hell, darling,
why don't you join us.

32:01.120 --> 32:03.387
If I'm not being
too forward, that is.

32:03.389 --> 32:05.088
- Actually, I am kinda hungry.

32:05.090 --> 32:06.290
Do you mind taking
me home after?

32:06.292 --> 32:09.726
- Well as long as Mr. Bambi
ain't gonna blow his lid.

32:09.728 --> 32:13.497
- Well, keep your lid on
daddio, there is no Mr. Bambi.

32:13.499 --> 32:15.198
- All the better, sweetie.

32:15.200 --> 32:17.834
(upbeat music)

32:36.855 --> 32:38.021
(dramatic music)

32:38.023 --> 32:39.589
- Hey, you need a ride?

32:39.591 --> 32:42.392
(dramatic music)

33:06.518 --> 33:10.654
- Yes, I have power like
none you have ever seen.

33:12.458 --> 33:15.325
Even stronger than Godzilla.

33:15.327 --> 33:17.394
We barbecue their asses.

33:18.697 --> 33:20.931
(tapping)

33:28.807 --> 33:31.541
(phone beeping)

33:35.280 --> 33:38.482
(crickets chirping)

33:38.484 --> 33:41.818
- This is Autumn, look hey,
when you get this message,

33:41.820 --> 33:44.721
I need you to send some
of the boys over here.

33:44.723 --> 33:46.323
I think those town motherfuckers

33:46.325 --> 33:47.791
are here again, messing around.

33:47.793 --> 33:49.026
(dramatic music)
I'm gonna--

33:49.028 --> 33:50.394
- You're not gonna need that.

33:50.396 --> 33:52.096
(Autumn gasping)
I'm the only lie

33:52.097 --> 33:53.797
you're gonna need.
(Ronnie cackling)

33:53.799 --> 33:57.901
And good news, I brought some
of the boys along with me.

33:57.903 --> 34:00.871
(Ronnie chuckling)

34:10.849 --> 34:12.949
- What the fuck is
wrong with you?

34:12.951 --> 34:17.154
- Well now, Autumn, you should
know what's wrong with us.

34:17.156 --> 34:22.225
You made us this way
and it's all your fault.

34:22.628 --> 34:26.830
If you'da just kept that nose
of yours out of my business,

34:26.832 --> 34:28.899
none of this would be
happening right now.

34:28.901 --> 34:33.970
And now we're here to make
sure you never do that again.

34:34.540 --> 34:36.740
(dramatic music)
(Ronnie cackling)

34:36.742 --> 34:39.076
- Such a pretty face.

34:39.078 --> 34:40.610
I think I'll take it with me.

34:41.847 --> 34:42.679
- Look, I'm sorry.

34:42.681 --> 34:44.714
Ronnie, Ronnie, Ronnie, Ron,

34:44.716 --> 34:46.583
I promise I'll stay
out of your business.

34:46.585 --> 34:49.419
I won't be in it anymore,
just please let me go.

34:49.421 --> 34:51.855
Please stop, stop please.

34:51.857 --> 34:53.457
- Can we shut that mug up?

34:53.459 --> 34:54.524
Come on, she's wailing

34:54.526 --> 34:55.859
like a frickin' police
- Oh fuck, I'm sorry.

34:55.861 --> 34:57.561
- siren over there.
- Ronnie, wait, I'm sorry.

34:57.563 --> 34:58.595
- Come on, do something.
- You're right,

34:58.597 --> 34:59.896
I should stay outta your--

34:59.898 --> 35:01.431
(Autumn screaming)

35:01.433 --> 35:04.201
(dramatic music)
(blood splattering)

35:04.203 --> 35:07.204
(clowns chuckling)

35:08.140 --> 35:11.041
(flesh squishing)

35:31.530 --> 35:34.164
(soft music)

35:34.166 --> 35:37.501
- So I left his cheating ass
and I went back to school.

35:37.503 --> 35:40.170
And of course,
school is very expensive.

35:40.172 --> 35:42.305
So, I tried to waitress a while.

35:42.307 --> 35:44.141
This very diner, to be exact.

35:45.010 --> 35:48.678
The tips were shitty and the
hourly is just insulting.

35:48.680 --> 35:50.347
If I was gonna make
it on my own.

35:50.349 --> 35:52.616
I was gonna have to
figure out something fast.

35:52.618 --> 35:55.252
So, I gave it a try, that's all.

35:55.254 --> 35:57.521
- Well, one thing's for sure,
you got the looks for it,

35:57.523 --> 36:00.657
and the moves to match
from I caught of that show.

36:00.659 --> 36:03.326
Man, I'm sure sorry
that had to happen.

36:03.328 --> 36:04.594
- So what you gonna do now?

36:04.596 --> 36:05.695
- Not sure.

36:05.697 --> 36:07.764
Hasn't really hit me yet.

36:07.766 --> 36:10.600
But when it does, I'll
probably have a good cry,

36:10.602 --> 36:12.702
and figure out the
best way I can.

36:12.704 --> 36:16.473
One thing about me,
baby, I'm a survivor.

36:16.475 --> 36:19.109
(bell dinging)

36:19.978 --> 36:22.045
- I'm so sorry, but
there's a creep out there

36:22.047 --> 36:25.015
and he's been following me for
miles and he tried to give me

36:25.017 --> 36:27.584
a ride and I told him no,
and he just keeps showing up.

36:27.586 --> 36:29.085
- You gotta be a freak to follow

36:29.087 --> 36:30.687
a little girl around like that.

36:32.624 --> 36:33.890
- Is that the guy?

36:34.893 --> 36:37.093
- Yeah, real creep.

36:37.095 --> 36:39.329
- Hey, y'all doin'?
- You've been wonderful.

36:39.331 --> 36:40.964
- Well, good.

36:40.966 --> 36:42.666
Okay, there you go.

36:42.668 --> 36:44.734
Order'll be up in just a sec.

36:44.736 --> 36:48.872
(people talking over each other)

36:57.282 --> 37:01.218
(light dramatic music)

37:01.220 --> 37:02.252
You okay, hun?

37:02.254 --> 37:03.887
You seen a little nervous or
something.

37:03.889 --> 37:04.854
- Yeah, I'm good.

37:04.856 --> 37:06.273
Thank you.

37:06.274 --> 37:07.691
- Haven't seen you
around here before.

37:07.693 --> 37:09.626
- Nobody's from around here.

37:09.628 --> 37:11.761
Isn't everyone just
passing through?

37:11.763 --> 37:13.630
- Well, you may
be right about that.

37:13.632 --> 37:16.066
- I'd take that check
when you have the chance.

37:18.403 --> 37:19.736
- Hey, buddy.

37:19.738 --> 37:21.738
Let's have a little chat.

37:21.740 --> 37:23.540
From where I see it,
you world's nothing

37:23.542 --> 37:25.175
but bad intentions, man.

37:25.177 --> 37:27.577
The way you're eyeballing
that young girl over there.

37:27.579 --> 37:28.878
- Look, man.

37:28.880 --> 37:30.046
I don't want any trouble.

37:30.048 --> 37:31.848
I just wanna get a cup of
freakin' coffee

37:31.850 --> 37:33.917
and play on my phone a bit.

37:33.919 --> 37:35.352
- Oh, is that so?

37:35.354 --> 37:38.788
Well that little lady over there
is pretty shaken up by you.

37:38.790 --> 37:41.391
Says you've been bugging
her, following her around.

37:42.261 --> 37:44.427
Why would she go and
lie on you like that?

37:46.632 --> 37:47.530
All right, pal.

37:47.532 --> 37:48.965
How about I buy you a beer.

37:48.967 --> 37:50.166
- Alcohol is bad news, man.

37:50.168 --> 37:53.470
It weakens the character,
fuzzes the brain.

37:53.472 --> 37:55.772
It makes you soft.

37:55.774 --> 37:57.674
I've been down that road before.

37:57.676 --> 38:00.176
It's full of nothing but
broken promises and pain.

38:00.178 --> 38:02.746
Hurting everyone that you
ever gave a damn about.

38:02.748 --> 38:04.114
No thanks, man.

38:04.116 --> 38:05.448
Keep your beer.

38:05.450 --> 38:07.350
- Oh, is that so?

38:07.352 --> 38:10.153
Well, it's moving time
around here, buddy,

38:10.155 --> 38:12.355
and I think you
should catch the fever.

38:12.357 --> 38:13.356
Get movin'.

38:14.259 --> 38:16.559
(thudding)

38:20.098 --> 38:21.097
Problem solved.

38:25.704 --> 38:28.772
(car door slamming)

38:31.410 --> 38:34.744
(light dramatic music)

38:46.325 --> 38:49.392
- So is the bus usually
on time around here?

38:49.394 --> 38:50.827
- Hell, honey,
I haven't taken a bus

38:50.829 --> 38:52.862
since I had pigtails
and poodle skirts.

38:57.069 --> 39:00.303
(wind whistling)

39:00.305 --> 39:02.238
(thunder booming)

39:02.240 --> 39:03.306
- Fucking wonderful.

39:04.676 --> 39:05.975
(zapping)

39:05.977 --> 39:07.811
- What the hell?
- What the hell?

39:07.813 --> 39:09.245
(people talking over each other)

39:09.247 --> 39:10.880
- What the hell is going on?

39:10.882 --> 39:12.515
- [Woman] We never know.

39:12.517 --> 39:15.418
(thunder booming)

39:21.860 --> 39:25.261
- You've gotta be
fucking kidding me.

39:25.263 --> 39:30.100
(dramatic music)
(wind whistling)

39:30.102 --> 39:32.869
Screw driver, crowbar,
hammer, anything.

39:32.871 --> 39:34.371
Fuck, fuck, fuck.

39:36.308 --> 39:38.508
(zapping)

39:41.980 --> 39:44.814
(dramatic music)

39:45.717 --> 39:49.753
(clowns chuckling)
(muffled talking)

39:49.755 --> 39:52.655
(Ronnie growling)

39:53.992 --> 39:55.959
- You know this clown, honey?

39:55.961 --> 39:57.093
- You could say that.

39:58.296 --> 40:03.366
(thunder booming)
(pounding)

40:05.303 --> 40:07.937
Hey, Flo, you got
the keys to that door?

40:07.939 --> 40:10.807
- Under the counter over
there, and the name's Alice.

40:10.809 --> 40:11.941
- Of course it is.

40:11.943 --> 40:13.176
Let's go with those
keys sweetie.

40:13.178 --> 40:15.612
You don't want these
fuckers in here, trust me.

40:16.481 --> 40:18.114
(pounding on door)

40:18.116 --> 40:19.382
(Ronnie chuckling)

40:19.384 --> 40:20.483
Get the fucking keys.

40:31.263 --> 40:32.896
- [Hunter] Come on.

40:38.570 --> 40:41.237
Yeah.

40:41.239 --> 40:44.073
(dramatic music)

40:46.077 --> 40:47.677
(clowns laughing)

40:47.679 --> 40:49.679
- Get in the back, all of you.

40:49.681 --> 40:51.948
Get in the back now, move.

40:51.950 --> 40:54.350
Move, move!
(Ronnie chuckling)

40:54.352 --> 40:55.819
Look for a phone.

40:56.988 --> 40:58.955
- Damn, I got nothing.

40:59.858 --> 41:01.090
- Yeah, nothing here either.

41:01.092 --> 41:03.026
Maybe the storm?

41:03.027 --> 41:04.961
