1:00:43.207 --> 1:00:45.440
- Shit's dead, man.

1:00:45.442 --> 1:00:47.009
- Dion, really?

1:00:47.011 --> 1:00:48.777
- I know, Captain Obvious,
right?

1:00:48.779 --> 1:00:50.812
- I'm just trying to be a good
Samaritan,

1:00:50.814 --> 1:00:52.748
and this shit happens.

1:00:52.750 --> 1:00:53.982
Nearest garage?

1:00:53.984 --> 1:00:56.618
- Did you hear me, shit for
brains?

1:00:56.620 --> 1:00:58.854
I don't have time to get a
deputy here.

1:00:58.856 --> 1:01:01.289
You are my backup.

1:01:01.291 --> 1:01:03.792
Now I am telling you, not
asking,

1:01:03.794 --> 1:01:06.862
get these people outta
here and to a safe place.

1:01:06.864 --> 1:01:08.130
Do you hear me?

1:01:08.132 --> 1:01:09.398
- Well what about you?

1:01:09.400 --> 1:01:10.666
Sheriff, you can't stay here,

1:01:10.668 --> 1:01:12.300
that shitstorm is coming this
way.

1:01:12.302 --> 1:01:15.170
- I'm gettin' my ass on the
road and alerting everyone--

1:01:15.172 --> 1:01:18.774
(whistling)
(thunder booming)

1:01:18.776 --> 1:01:21.109
- [Hunter] Come on.

1:01:21.111 --> 1:01:22.444
Hey, come here.

1:01:24.114 --> 1:01:28.617
- [Bambi] You got room for me?.

1:01:28.619 --> 1:01:30.686
- All right, go, go, go.

1:01:35.893 --> 1:01:37.292
Son of a bitch, you clowns.

1:01:38.562 --> 1:01:41.463
(clowns cackling)

1:01:43.133 --> 1:01:45.767
(swanky music)

1:02:00.384 --> 1:02:02.084
- Well hello, nurse.

1:02:02.086 --> 1:02:03.852
Where have you been hiding,
honey?

1:02:10.594 --> 1:02:11.893
You okay, honey?

1:02:11.895 --> 1:02:13.695
I know the circus is in town.

1:02:21.105 --> 1:02:24.673
(groaning)
(dramatic music)

1:02:24.675 --> 1:02:26.475
Bitch, what the fuck?

1:02:27.377 --> 1:02:28.443
Shit!
(Savanna laughing)

1:02:28.445 --> 1:02:29.277
(woman gasping)

1:02:29.279 --> 1:02:34.349
(blood squishing)
(woman groaning)

1:02:37.721 --> 1:02:39.755
- Fuckin' die already!

1:02:40.791 --> 1:02:43.658
(thunder booming)

1:02:47.264 --> 1:02:51.600
- This little piggy went to
hell.

1:02:52.536 --> 1:02:54.503
(Ronnie cackling)

1:02:54.505 --> 1:02:55.403
Oh, yeah.

1:02:57.741 --> 1:03:00.742
- I don't know where
the hell you came from.

1:03:01.578 --> 1:03:05.313
Probably the sewer, but
I suggest you all go back

1:03:05.315 --> 1:03:07.516
there before my backup arrives.

1:03:07.518 --> 1:03:10.886
- Oh, you mean these all-day
suckers?

1:03:10.888 --> 1:03:13.789
(clowns laughing)

1:03:16.426 --> 1:03:19.127
Hey, calm down kid.

1:03:19.129 --> 1:03:20.996
Buy yourself an orchid.

1:03:20.998 --> 1:03:22.664
(laughing)

1:03:22.666 --> 1:03:24.766
- They were so much fun.

1:03:24.768 --> 1:03:29.671
- There's only room for one
Sheriff in this town, partner.

1:03:30.607 --> 1:03:33.608
(Satchel laughing)

1:03:38.048 --> 1:03:41.082
(suspenseful music)

1:03:46.490 --> 1:03:49.624
(flesh squishing)
(Sheriff yelling)

1:03:49.626 --> 1:03:51.059
Oh, yeah!

1:03:51.061 --> 1:03:52.861
Rip that piggy apart.

1:03:54.231 --> 1:03:56.164
Oh yeah, I smell bacon.

1:03:56.166 --> 1:03:57.799
Yeah, burn in hell.

1:04:02.072 --> 1:04:05.106
I'm gonna munch on his little,
(groaning).

1:04:05.108 --> 1:04:06.775
Mm, let's have bacon in the
morning.

1:04:06.777 --> 1:04:08.743
(Ronnie laughing)

1:04:08.745 --> 1:04:09.644
Yeah.

1:04:13.417 --> 1:04:16.318
(blood squishing)

1:04:33.036 --> 1:04:35.804
- We've been chasing
storms for a long time now,

1:04:35.806 --> 1:04:38.640
and we've never seen anything
like this.

1:04:38.642 --> 1:04:40.375
- Someone needs to come
out with the goods here,

1:04:40.377 --> 1:04:42.377
and you better lay it on my
fast before that screwed up

1:04:42.379 --> 1:04:44.880
twister comes back, and we're
all having this conversation

1:04:44.882 --> 1:04:47.115
from a bunch of pine boxes
down on Forrest Lawn.

1:04:47.117 --> 1:04:49.618
- Those fuckin' things they
ride around in that tornado

1:04:49.620 --> 1:04:52.187
like it's a DeLorean that just
came back from the future.

1:04:52.189 --> 1:04:53.521
And when they get done,

1:04:53.523 --> 1:04:56.124
most people they meet
aren't breathing anymore.

1:04:56.126 --> 1:04:57.025
Do you get it?

1:04:57.928 --> 1:04:59.628
- Breaker one three, breaker one
three,

1:04:59.630 --> 1:05:02.464
Rusty, can you hear us, Rusty?

1:05:02.466 --> 1:05:05.634
(static buzzing)

1:05:05.636 --> 1:05:07.168
- Am I not speaking English?

1:05:07.170 --> 1:05:09.738
You people are the only way
I can home to my daughter.

1:05:09.740 --> 1:05:11.239
She is probably freaking the
hell out right about now,

1:05:11.241 --> 1:05:13.208
and we are sitting here like
idiots.

1:05:13.210 --> 1:05:15.210
Check that thing while we drive.

1:05:15.212 --> 1:05:17.512
That tornado is gonna
popup any fuckin' minute.

1:05:17.514 --> 1:05:20.215
- I just wish I knew what
the hell we're dealing with.

1:05:21.084 --> 1:05:22.884
(wailing)

1:05:22.886 --> 1:05:25.186
- Oh and I guess we have to
deal with this shit again.

1:05:25.188 --> 1:05:27.055
Fuck!

1:05:27.056 --> 1:05:28.923
- Look sister, those
motherfuckers are relentless.

1:05:28.926 --> 1:05:30.125
They don't stop coming.

1:05:31.128 --> 1:05:33.962
(dramatic music)

1:05:34.831 --> 1:05:36.431
- Thanks for the ride, bitch.

1:05:40.671 --> 1:05:43.571
(thunder booming)

1:05:50.414 --> 1:05:52.614
- Chris, we need to find some
cover.

1:05:52.616 --> 1:05:53.782
That thing's getting bigger.

1:05:53.784 --> 1:05:55.617
I don't know if we're gonna out
run it.

1:05:55.619 --> 1:05:57.452
- We need to figure out
how to stop this shit.

1:05:57.454 --> 1:06:00.121
That thing's big enough to turn
this whole town upside down.

1:06:00.123 --> 1:06:02.524
- There's no way to stop
a tornado, Einstein.

1:06:02.526 --> 1:06:04.759
- Actually, there's a theory

1:06:04.761 --> 1:06:07.729
and it's been proven by some
scientists.

1:06:07.731 --> 1:06:10.832
A tornado is pretty complex,
but there has to be a perfect

1:06:10.834 --> 1:06:13.001
mix of hot and cold to
make it work, right?

1:06:13.003 --> 1:06:14.369
- I get it, Molly.

1:06:14.371 --> 1:06:16.004
A tornado needs both a cold
downdraft

1:06:16.006 --> 1:06:17.973
and a warm updraft in order to
form.

1:06:17.975 --> 1:06:19.308
If you take one of those away,

1:06:19.309 --> 1:06:20.642
then the whole thing becomes
unstable.

1:06:20.644 --> 1:06:22.310
Holy shit, I think I got an
idea.

1:06:22.312 --> 1:06:24.179
- So how did they stop a
tornado?

1:06:24.181 --> 1:06:25.146
Get to the point.

1:06:25.148 --> 1:06:29.751
- They used liquid nitrogen
to cool the whole thing down.

1:06:29.753 --> 1:06:31.519
- Liquid nitrogen?

1:06:31.521 --> 1:06:34.356
- My uncle, he owns an ice cream
shop.

1:06:34.358 --> 1:06:36.891
He uses liquid nitrogen
to make his own shit.

1:06:36.893 --> 1:06:38.360
I just need to get us there.

1:06:39.429 --> 1:06:40.729
He's got the whole rig.

1:06:40.731 --> 1:06:42.897
A vacuum storage tank, the
works.

1:06:42.899 --> 1:06:45.467
We just have to figure out
how to get it in the tornado.

1:06:45.469 --> 1:06:48.069
- Yeah, I might be able to help
you there.

1:06:48.071 --> 1:06:51.373
(dramatic music)

1:06:51.375 --> 1:06:53.742
(wind whistling)

1:06:53.744 --> 1:06:54.642
- Dammit.

1:06:58.715 --> 1:07:00.949
This is bullshit.

1:07:00.951 --> 1:07:04.652
(electric zapping)

1:07:04.654 --> 1:07:06.388
- Fuck.
(Bambi groaning)

1:07:06.390 --> 1:07:09.257
Look dude, get the fuck outta
here.

1:07:09.259 --> 1:07:12.093
(tires screeching)

1:07:12.095 --> 1:07:13.745
(horn honking)

1:07:13.746 --> 1:07:15.396
- [Chris] You've gotta
be fucking kidding me.

1:07:16.433 --> 1:07:20.201
(clown grunting)
(screaming)

1:07:20.203 --> 1:07:21.102
- Oh, God!

1:07:25.108 --> 1:07:26.941
- Get the fuck down.

1:07:26.943 --> 1:07:29.077
Now show me that smile,
buttercup.

1:07:29.913 --> 1:07:33.281
(dramatic music)

1:07:33.283 --> 1:07:35.216
Yes, these freaks can die.

1:07:35.986 --> 1:07:38.286
- I'm really glad you
knew how to use that.

1:07:41.358 --> 1:07:43.625
(squirting)

1:07:43.627 --> 1:07:46.261
- Oh, Ronnie's gonna be pissed.

1:07:49.166 --> 1:07:51.966
(dramatic music)

1:07:56.206 --> 1:07:58.940
- Well, how you doin',
doll face?

1:08:00.110 --> 1:08:02.477
(swanky music)

1:08:02.479 --> 1:08:04.312
No hard feelings, right?

1:08:05.415 --> 1:08:06.815
- From where I stand, you smell
like

1:08:06.817 --> 1:08:09.084
a pitiful excuse for a man.

1:08:09.086 --> 1:08:12.487
The stench wraps around my
throat and makes me wanna
wretch.

1:08:12.489 --> 1:08:16.524
Hard feelings, baby, I've got
the hardest.

1:08:16.526 --> 1:08:17.425
- Motherfucker.

1:08:18.295 --> 1:08:19.394
- Don't get your panties wet,

1:08:19.396 --> 1:08:21.563
sweetheart, I'm not the dancing
type.

1:08:21.565 --> 1:08:24.632
(Satchel giggling)

1:08:24.634 --> 1:08:27.535
(flesh squishing)

1:08:29.272 --> 1:08:32.173
(blood squirting)

1:08:33.176 --> 1:08:36.077
(Satchel gasping)

1:08:37.814 --> 1:08:40.148
(Satchel coughing)

1:08:40.150 --> 1:08:41.683
(Savanna groaning)

1:08:41.685 --> 1:08:44.752
(Savanna screaming)

1:08:46.356 --> 1:08:48.923
(Ronnie groaning)
(bones snapping)

1:08:48.925 --> 1:08:51.826
(clowns laughing)

1:08:52.596 --> 1:08:55.497
(Ronnie cackling)

1:08:58.268 --> 1:09:01.236
(Satchel screaming)

1:09:01.238 --> 1:09:02.804
(Satchel coughing)

1:09:02.806 --> 1:09:05.640
(clown growling)

1:09:11.081 --> 1:09:13.481
(squishing)

1:09:21.858 --> 1:09:24.792
- It's so hard to say goodbye,
Chuckles.

1:09:33.570 --> 1:09:34.936
Watch the bitch.

1:09:35.872 --> 1:09:38.606
I wanna make sure she's
really dead this time.

1:09:40.143 --> 1:09:41.910
Come on, Wizzo.

1:09:41.912 --> 1:09:44.579
There's much to do before
sunrise.

1:09:44.581 --> 1:09:45.914
Someone took one of ours.

1:09:47.884 --> 1:09:50.018
And revenge is in the air, boys.

1:09:50.020 --> 1:09:52.453
(Wizzo whimpering)

1:09:52.455 --> 1:09:55.290
(dramatic music)

1:09:58.828 --> 1:10:01.396
(suspenseful music)

1:10:01.398 --> 1:10:04.199
(Chris groaning)

1:10:05.168 --> 1:10:07.702
- Damn, too bad the phones
are still messed up.

1:10:07.704 --> 1:10:09.003
We could have made one phone
call

1:10:09.005 --> 1:10:10.838
and wouldn't have had to do any
of this.

1:10:10.840 --> 1:10:13.241
- Molly, you got the goods?

1:10:18.515 --> 1:10:20.181
Cover your ears.

1:10:20.183 --> 1:10:23.051
(gunshot banging)

1:10:23.053 --> 1:10:24.586
Not so bad, come on.

1:10:26.456 --> 1:10:29.757
(light dramatic music)

1:10:44.207 --> 1:10:45.106
Hunter.

1:10:46.543 --> 1:10:48.509
I found it.

1:10:48.511 --> 1:10:50.445
Only chance we got, really.

1:10:50.447 --> 1:10:54.749
- Okay, if we're gonna do
this, we don't drop it,

1:10:54.751 --> 1:10:58.152
we don't shake it, we don't
even sneeze around this thing,

1:10:58.154 --> 1:11:00.188
or they're gonna picking
up pieces of all of us

1:11:00.190 --> 1:11:02.890
all the way back to Texas, get
it?

1:11:02.892 --> 1:11:05.493
(Rachel crying)
- I'm such an asshole.

1:11:05.495 --> 1:11:09.230
I shoulda called my mom when
I had the chance and I didn't.

1:11:10.400 --> 1:11:12.066
I fucked everything up.

1:11:13.069 --> 1:11:16.104
- Oh, honey, it'll be okay.

1:11:16.106 --> 1:11:17.538
- Rachel, look at me.

1:11:18.408 --> 1:11:20.341
We're gonna get you home, okay?

1:11:20.343 --> 1:11:22.143
You and Bambi both.

1:11:22.145 --> 1:11:23.378
We're gonna be okay.

1:11:23.380 --> 1:11:24.712
(thunder booming)
(Molly hushing)

1:11:24.714 --> 1:11:25.613
- Listen.

1:11:27.083 --> 1:11:27.915
(thudding)

1:11:27.917 --> 1:11:29.083
What the hell is that?

1:11:30.120 --> 1:11:31.853
- Thunder, motherfucker,
thunder.

1:11:32.722 --> 1:11:35.056
- Chris, we need a cart or
something.

1:11:36.693 --> 1:11:37.592
- Will this do?

1:11:42.098 --> 1:11:44.666
(clanking)

1:11:44.668 --> 1:11:47.468
(dramatic music)

1:11:52.942 --> 1:11:57.245
(intense dramatic music)
- Oh hell.

1:12:01.318 --> 1:12:02.150
(thudding)
- Oh, Dion!

1:12:02.152 --> 1:12:04.686
(screaming)

1:12:04.688 --> 1:12:05.787
- Oh, my God.
- Dion!

1:12:05.789 --> 1:12:07.088
- Dion, Dion!
- Oh, no!

1:12:07.090 --> 1:12:08.723
(clown cackling)

1:12:08.725 --> 1:12:12.160
(gunshot banging)

1:12:12.162 --> 1:12:13.961
(light dramatic music)

1:12:13.963 --> 1:12:16.864
(Hunter groaning)

1:12:31.448 --> 1:12:36.517
(dramatic music)
(clowns laughing)

1:12:51.368 --> 1:12:53.801
(Savanna gasping)

1:12:53.803 --> 1:12:54.702
- Oh.

1:12:58.108 --> 1:13:00.208
(neck cracking)

1:13:00.210 --> 1:13:01.442
Mother fucker.

1:13:04.748 --> 1:13:07.215
(thunder booming)

1:13:07.217 --> 1:13:12.220
Ronnie, the bitch is back,
and she's comin' to get ya.

1:13:12.222 --> 1:13:15.022
(dramatic music)

1:13:17.560 --> 1:13:18.926
- [Hunter] Where the hell are
we?

1:13:18.928 --> 1:13:21.796
- My uncle's shop is
attached to an old mini-mall.

1:13:21.798 --> 1:13:23.798
- Got any gun stores?

1:13:23.800 --> 1:13:25.133
- No.

1:13:25.135 --> 1:13:26.567
Fucking idiot.

1:13:26.569 --> 1:13:28.836
Using all that ammo on the
goddamn door.

1:13:28.838 --> 1:13:30.838
- Shit, it's not on you.

1:13:30.840 --> 1:13:34.909
Shit happens and today shit
happens every 42 seconds.

1:13:34.911 --> 1:13:36.878
We just gotta get this thing to
the truck.

1:13:36.880 --> 1:13:38.212
Number one priority.

1:13:39.048 --> 1:13:40.648
- I think we can get out through
here.

1:13:53.163 --> 1:13:54.061
(elevator dinging)

1:13:54.063 --> 1:13:55.863
We need to get to the parking
garage.

1:13:55.865 --> 1:13:56.697
That's our way out.

1:13:56.699 --> 1:13:57.765
- Sounds good to me.

1:14:00.703 --> 1:14:01.602
Easy now.

1:14:10.146 --> 1:14:12.613
(dramatic music)
(screaming)

1:14:12.615 --> 1:14:14.949
- No!
- Here's Chuckles.

1:14:14.951 --> 1:14:16.617
(Chuckles giggling)

1:14:16.619 --> 1:14:17.652
- No!

1:14:17.654 --> 1:14:19.654
- Hunter, get 'em outta here.

1:14:19.656 --> 1:14:21.022
- Dion!
- TCB, baby.

1:14:22.859 --> 1:14:24.525
- Well, well, well.

1:14:25.595 --> 1:14:28.996
Elvis, I'm such a big fan.

1:14:33.036 --> 1:14:36.137
(clowns laughing)

1:14:36.139 --> 1:14:37.672
(thudding)
(squishing)

1:14:37.674 --> 1:14:40.508
(Dion screaming)

1:14:49.619 --> 1:14:54.689
(Ronnie chuckling)
(suspenseful music)

1:14:58.161 --> 1:15:00.828
Elvis has left the building.

1:15:00.830 --> 1:15:03.731
(Ronnie laughing)

1:15:09.305 --> 1:15:13.040
(suspenseful music)

1:15:13.042 --> 1:15:15.209
(thudding)

1:15:15.211 --> 1:15:16.110
- Shit.

1:15:27.390 --> 1:15:28.723
This is bullshit.

1:15:28.725 --> 1:15:29.824
Dammit.

1:15:29.826 --> 1:15:31.459
- Shit, Chris, they're coming.

1:15:31.461 --> 1:15:34.095
(creepy music)

1:15:34.964 --> 1:15:38.599
(clowns grunting)

1:15:38.601 --> 1:15:41.502
- Chris, give me a
hand with this.

1:15:45.375 --> 1:15:46.374
Yeah, good.

1:15:47.176 --> 1:15:48.042
Hey you get the rig.

1:15:48.044 --> 1:15:49.176
- [Chris] Everything I got.

1:15:49.178 --> 1:15:51.712
- Those circus freaks will
be here any minute now.

1:15:56.519 --> 1:15:57.552
- All right, slowly.
- Careful.

1:16:01.858 --> 1:16:03.791
- You're gonna have
to get in first.

1:16:03.793 --> 1:16:05.426
- All right, watch out.

1:16:07.030 --> 1:16:08.429
- Rachel, Bambi.

1:16:17.240 --> 1:16:19.740
Hey, hotshot, you wanna
take the back for cover?

1:16:19.742 --> 1:16:22.743
- Already in the plan, my
man, I'm your Huckleberry.

1:16:22.745 --> 1:16:24.145
- Damn, girl, I think I'm in
love.

1:16:24.147 --> 1:16:26.447
Another time and another place,
right?

1:16:26.449 --> 1:16:28.382
Be sure to put the grill back.

1:16:29.953 --> 1:16:31.285
(clowns chuckling)

1:16:31.287 --> 1:16:33.588
- [Wizzo] Yeah, god dammit.

1:16:42.532 --> 1:16:45.600
(suspenseful music)

1:16:47.971 --> 1:16:52.306
- I wish none of this
was happening, but it is.

1:16:53.376 --> 1:16:55.176
And we gotta stay strong.

1:16:57.313 --> 1:16:59.246
We're almost there.

1:16:59.248 --> 1:17:02.083
- [Molly] That's some real
uplifting shit, right there.

1:17:04.020 --> 1:17:05.286
(clowns laughing)

1:17:05.288 --> 1:17:06.187
- Intense.

1:17:09.125 --> 1:17:10.024
You, hey.

1:17:11.094 --> 1:17:12.126
You're up.

1:17:12.128 --> 1:17:12.960
- No I won't.

1:17:12.962 --> 1:17:13.794
- Yeah.
- No.

1:17:13.796 --> 1:17:15.029
- Yeah, you.
- What, no.

1:17:15.031 --> 1:17:16.831
- Well I guess if you
want something done right

1:17:16.833 --> 1:17:18.132
you gotta do it yourself.

1:17:18.134 --> 1:17:20.368
(Ronnie growling)
Turn back.

